{"tid":1126104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【單車亞洲賽】新星李思穎為港開齋奪金　港隊女青個人公路賽冧莊","createTime":"2019-04-26T06:44:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T07:12:41.000Z","uid":241764,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d3dc16be6e37d48ec34fd5c475f4b4fe94825d06","tid":1126104,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T06:44:14.000Z","msg":"香港單車隊於公路單車亞洲賽戰至第4天，今日憑新星李思穎於女子青年個人公路賽封后，摘下今屆第一金，亦是港隊連續兩年稱霸此項目。<br />\n<br />\n賽事今日續於烏茲別克上演，已奪7面銅牌的港隊，派出衛冕的趙蕙芸，伙李思穎、許逸雅及梁悅，合力出戰女子青年個人公路賽，最終李思穎力壓日本隊、蒙古隊等多國車手，在62.4公里路程率先衝線，為港奪走今屆首金。18歲的李思穎連同個人公路計時賽，獨攬1金1銅。<br />\n<br />\n港隊明日轉戰女子成年組個人公路賽，衝金以換取明年東京奧運入場券。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2/article/20190426/s00006/1556257148671/%E3%80%90%E5%96%AE%E8%BB%8A%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2%E8%B3%BD%E3%80%91%E6%96%B0%E6%98%9F%E6%9D%8E%E6%80%9D%E7%A9%8E%E7%82%BA%E6%B8%AF%E9%96%8B%E9%BD%8B%E5%A5%AA%E9%87%91-%E6%B8%AF%E9%9A%8A%E5%A5%B3%E9%9D%92%E5%80%8B%E4%BA%BA%E5%85%AC%E8%B7%AF%E8%B3%BD%E5%86%A7%E8%8E%8A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E9%25AB%2594%25E8%2582%25B2%2Farticle%2F20190426%2Fs00006%2F1556257148671%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%2596%25AE%25E8%25BB%258A%25E4%25BA%259E%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E8%25B3%25BD%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%2598%259F%25E6%259D%258E%25E6%2580%259D%25E7%25A9%258E%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2596%258B%25E9%25BD%258B%25E5%25A5%25AA%25E9%2587%2591-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%259A%258A%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E9%259D%2592%25E5%2580%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2585%25AC%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E8%25B3%25BD%25E5%2586%25A7%25E8%258E%258A&d=tLsEO8KpRnvfRHW%2FlT3TjvsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=8ad06eb3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E9%25AB%2594%25E8%2582%25B2%2Farticle%2F20190426%2Fs00006%2F1556257148671%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%2596%25AE%25E8%25BB%258A%25E4%25BA%259E%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E8%25B3%25BD%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%2598%259F%25E6%259D%258E%25E6%2580%259D%25